room_title: Escape room "Amnesia" by Michigan Escape Room in Detroit
room_address: 58944 Van Dyke Ave. Washington Twp., MI 48094
room_description: You've been asked to be part of what you thought, a harmless government experiment.  You quickly learn it's  more than you bargained for .  As you slowly start to lose parts of your memory, you race to escape the lab before your memory is gone for good. But first, you must complete the tests in time!
